node.text:

node.text:
Folks, we have a real crisis at our border. We shot this footage at 1AM in the border town of Roma, Texas. Please watch and share.

Leaders go to the frontlines to assess a problem. Leaders lead 24/7, being a governor is not a 9-5 job. 

This crisis at our border is one of the reasons I am fighting for you. Will you join me in Defending the Texas Republic?

For more about Allen West see:

Donate: https://west4texas.com/donation-form/
Campaign website: https://West4Texas.com 
Facebook Fan Page: https://fb.com/AllenBWest
Facebook Campaign Page: https://fb.com/West4Texas 
Twitter (personal): https://twitter.com/AllenWest 
Twitter (campaign): https://twitter.com/West4Texas.com
Instagram: https://instagram.com/allenbwest

node.text:
If everyone who follows me on social media gave just FIVE dollars each month leading up to the Primary, we would have a massive war chest against the progressive socialist leftist machine.

If you are so inclined -- and able to do so -- please give at https://bit.ly/W4Tgive

Everyone can do something to help us win: pray, give, share our content on social media, endorse me, or tell a friend! See more at West4Texas.com.

Whatever you are able to do, please know I will put #TexasFirst!
